          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="label">facebook</span>
            <a href="https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=61587960190805" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><svg class="icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="14" height="14"><path fill="currentColor" d="M24 12.073c0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12s-12 5.373-12 12c0 5.99 4.388 10.954 10.125 11.854v-8.385H7.078v-3.47h3.047V9.43c0-3.007 1.792-4.669 4.533-4.669 1.312 0 2.686.235 2.686.235v2.953H15.83c-1.491 0-1.956.925-1.956 1.874v2.25h3.328l-.532 3.47h-2.796v8.385C19.612 23.027 24 18.062 24 12.073z"/></svg> Headius</a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="label">bluesky</span>
